      • transformEntity

        protected Object transformEntity(int transform,
                                 GlobalTagCategory entity)
        Allows transformation of entities into value objects (or something else for that matter), when the transform flag is set to one of the constants defined in com.communote.server.persistence.tag.GlobalTagCategoryDao, please note that the GlobalTagCategoryDao.TRANSFORM_NONE constant denotes no transformation, so the entity itself will be returned.

        This method will return instances of these types:

        • GlobalTagCategory - GlobalTagCategoryDao.TRANSFORM_NONE
        • GlobalTagCategoryVO - TRANSFORM_GLOBALTAGCATEGORYVO
        If the integer argument value is unknown GlobalTagCategoryDao.TRANSFORM_NONE is assumed.
        Parameters:
        transform - one of the constants declared in GlobalTagCategoryDao
        entity - an entity that was found
        Returns:
        the transformed entity (i.e. new value object, etc)
        See Also:
        transformEntities(int,java.util.Collection)
